Package: VcfAssociation
Title: VCF Reading, Annotation, Association, and Visualization
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("X Li", "xiaof.li@utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")
Description: Read VCFs, merge phenotypes, annotate variants, run single-variant GWAS,
    and perform single-variant/gene associations (GLM or Firth), with visualization.
